'''唐納·霍華德·薩頓'''（{{lang-en|Donald Howard Sutton}}，{{bd|1945年|4月2日|2021年|1月19日|catIdx=Sutton}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的投手。生涯23年有16年效力於洛杉磯道奇，不過從未拿下冠軍。生涯曾效力過道奇、太空人、釀酒人、運動家與天使等隊。<ref name=BR>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/s/suttodo01.shtml|title=Don Sutton Statistics and History|publisher=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2013-11-16|archive-date=2011-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110808182535/http://www.baseball-reference.com/players/s/suttodo01.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>職業生涯累積324勝與3574次三振，後來他於1998年入選名人堂。

==職業生涯==
===生涯初期===
薩頓在1966年4月14日登上大聯盟<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.baseball-almanac.com/players/playerpost.php?p=suttodo01&ps=asg |title=Don Sutton All-Star Stats by Baseball Almanac |publisher=Baseball-almanac.com |date=1966-04-14 |access-date=2013-11-16 |archive-date=2021-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113135059/https://www.baseball-almanac.com/players/playerpost.php?p=suttodo01&ps=asg |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1970年代起，薩頓入選四次明星賽。1974年國聯冠軍賽，他一個人就貢獻了兩勝，幫助道奇打敗海盜。<ref name=LCS1974>{{cite web|title=1974 League Championship Series|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1974_NLCS.shtml|publisher=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|access-date=February 2, 2014|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112041907/http://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1974_NLCS.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在世界大賽拿下了道奇隊唯一的一勝。1976年，薩頓投出生涯年。該年他拿下21勝10敗。1977年世界大賽，薩頓先發兩場，其中一場還投出完投勝。可惜道奇最終仍敗下陣來。

1978年8月，薩頓曾在媒體面前說道：「Reggie Smith是我遇過表現最好的球員。」結果造成隊友[[史蒂夫·賈維|史蒂夫·賈維]]的不滿。他們兩人後來在面對大都會的比賽中打架，最後雙雙被禁賽處分。這年薩頓雖然投出15勝11敗，球隊也將他帶進季後賽行列中。<ref name=Fimrite>{{cite news|last=Fimrite|first=Ron|title=God may be a football fan|url=http://si.com/vault/article/magazine/MAG1125690/1/index.htm|access-date=February 2, 2014|newspaper=[[Sports_Illustrated|Sports Illustrated]]|date=July 12, 1982|archive-date=2014-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219132615/http://si.com/vault/article/magazine/MAG1125690/1/index.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>不過他在世界大賽卻投得綁手綁腳，最後道奇又再一次輸給洋基。<ref name=BR/>

===生涯後期===
1980年球季結束後，薩頓成為自由球員。<ref name=Bangor>{{cite news|title=A's trade Don Sutton to California Angels|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=2457&dat=19850911&id=oP9aAAAAIBAJ&pg=5564,4653426|access-date=February 2, 2014|newspaper=[[Bangor_Daily_News|Bangor Daily News]]|date=September 11, 1985|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111060543/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=2457&dat=19850911&id=oP9aAAAAIBAJ&pg=5564,4653426|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在隔年加入太空人，不過他卻在10月2日傷到了髕骨而提前退場。雖然太空人闖進季後賽，不過在少了薩頓的情況下還是早早被淘汰。<ref name=Rappoport>{{cite news|last=Rappoport|first=Ken|title=Astros lose game, and Don Sutton|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1915&dat=19811003&id=-HUfAAAAIBAJ&pg=3194,593512|access-date=February 2, 2014|newspaper=[[The_Day_(New_London)|The Day (New London)]]|date=October 3, 1981|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111070408/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1915&dat=19811003&id=-HUfAAAAIBAJ&pg=3194,593512|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1982年世界大賽，薩頓在10局投球內容中失9分，並吞下一敗。<ref name=BR/>釀酒人最終以3勝4敗輸給紅雀。

1982年球季末，太空人將薩頓交易至釀酒人，換來Kevin Bass、Frank DiPino和Mike Madden。<ref name=Trades>{{cite web|title=Don Sutton Trades and Transactions|url=http://www.baseball-almanac.com/players/trades.php?p=suttodo01|publisher=[[Baseball_Almanac|Baseball Almanac]]|access-date=February 2, 2014|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113120213/https://www.baseball-almanac.com/players/trades.php?p=suttodo01|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1985年，運動家用Ray Burris向釀酒人交易薩頓。當時薩頓以累積280勝，最後他拿下13勝8敗。<ref name=Newhan>{{cite news|last=Newhan|first=Ross|title=Don Sutton swallows his threat, reports to the A's camp|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1985-03-12/sports/sp-34291_1_don-sutton|access-date=February 2, 2014|newspaper=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|date=March 12, 1985|archive-date=2014-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140225024523/http://articles.latimes.com/1985-03-12/sports/sp-34291_1_don-sutton|dead-url=no}}</ref>而他在運動家僅待了1個球季，最後他在球季結束後被交易至天使，換來一名日後指定球員。<ref name=Bangor/>

1986年球季開打前，薩頓已經累積295勝。雖然他在球季初表現不太穩定，不過他仍在6月18日拿下生涯300勝。<ref name=Cress>{{cite news|last=Cress|first=Doug|title=Grateful Sutton savors 300th win|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1986-06-20/sports/8602140239_1_don-sutton-300th-dodgers|access-date=February 2, 2014|newspaper=[[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]]|date=June 20, 1986|archive-date=2014-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203143954/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1986-06-20/sports/8602140239_1_don-sutton-300th-dodgers|dead-url=no}}</ref>1986年美國聯盟冠軍賽，薩頓替天使隊出賽2場，最終都無關勝敗。<ref name=BR/>而天使也以3勝4敗輸給紅襪，無緣晉級世界大賽。

到了1988年，薩頓又與道奇隊簽約。8月時，太空人曾與薩頓見面，並詢問薩頓是否有意願擔任球隊的總經理。<ref name=McManis>{{cite news|last=McManis|first=Sam|title=Against Claire's wishes, Sutton talks to Astros|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1988-08-10/sports/sp-274_1_sutton-talks|access-date=February 2, 2014|newspaper=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|date=August 10, 1988|archive-date=2014-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228050908/http://articles.latimes.com/1988-08-10/sports/sp-274_1_sutton-talks|dead-url=no}}</ref>結果道奇隊副主席認為薩頓此舉已違反球隊規定，於是在8月10日將他釋出。<ref name=Cut>{{cite news|title=Dodgers cut 43-year-old Don Sutton|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1310&dat=19880811&id=gehVAAAAIBAJ&pg=5821,2405220|access-date=February 2, 2014|newspaper=[[Eugene_Register-Guard|Eugene Register-Guard]]|date=August 11, 1988|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111070027/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1310&dat=19880811&id=gehVAAAAIBAJ&pg=5821,2405220|dead-url=no}}</ref>他也因此離開大聯盟的舞台。

薩頓生涯也累積了不少特別的數據，像是生涯面對芝加哥小熊連敗13場，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.baseballlibrary.com/ballplayers/player.php?name=don_sutton_1945&page=chronology |title=The Ballplayers – Don Sutton |publisher=BaseballLibrary.com |access-date=2013-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140220025908/http://www.baseballlibrary.com/ballplayers/player.php?name=don_sutton_1945&page=chronology |archive-date=2014-02-20 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>還有7次完封對手卻都無關勝敗的大聯盟紀錄。
