==榮譽==
[[File:LAret20.PNG|thumb]]
1997年，已經進入第四年名人堂票選的薩頓原本被認為會成功入選名人堂，但最後卻以9票擦身而過。<ref name=Fame>{{cite news|last=Smith|first=Claire|title=When fame takes a back seat|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1997/01/28/sports/when-fame-takes-a-back-seat.html|access-date=February 2, 2014|newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=January 28, 1997|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111043107/https://www.nytimes.com/1997/01/28/sports/when-fame-takes-a-back-seat.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>後來到了隔年，薩頓終於順利入選名人堂，並成為該年唯一一位入選的選手。<ref name=Blum>{{cite news|last=Blum|first=Ronald|title=Hall Opens Its Doors For Sutton|url=http://www.spokesman.com/stories/1998/jan/06/hall-opens-its-doors-for-sutton/|access-date=February 2, 2014|newspaper=[[The_Spokesman-Review|The Spokesman-Review]]|date=January 6, 1998|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112090238/https://www.spokesman.com/stories/1998/jan/06/hall-opens-its-doors-for-sutton/|dead-url=no}}</ref>道奇隊也在同一年退休他的20號球衣。<ref name=Numbers>{{cite web|title=Dodgers Retired Numbers|url=http://losangeles.dodgers.mlb.com/la/history/retired_numbers.jsp|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|access-date=February 2, 2014|archive-date=2013-06-22|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6HYVhl6xu?url=http://losangeles.dodgers.mlb.com/la/history/retired_numbers.jsp|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年7月，當時在勇士隊擔任廣播員的薩頓入選勇士隊名人堂，成為勇士隊第四位以廣播員入選球隊名人堂的人物。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bain|first1=Matthew|title=Sutton inducted to Braves Hall of Fame|url=http://www.ajc.com/news/sports/baseball/sutton-inducted-to-braves-hall-of-fame/nm3hN/|access-date=July 21, 2015|work=Atlanta Journal Constitution|date=July 20, 2015|archive-date=2016-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160429013502/http://www.ajc.com/news/sports/baseball/sutton-inducted-to-braves-hall-of-fame/nm3hN/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
==去世==
2021年1月18日，薩頓因為癌症去世，享年75歲。<ref name=AP>{{cite news|title=Don Sutton, Hall of Fame pitcher for Dodgers, dies at 75|url=https://apnews.com/article/mlb-baseball-los-angeles-atlanta-braves-al-kaline-8319160f2989c94468612a9d30c87318|first=Beth|last=Harris|date=January 20, 2021|accessdate=January 20, 2021|agency=Associated Press|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120012401/https://apnews.com/article/mlb-baseball-los-angeles-atlanta-braves-al-kaline-8319160f2989c94468612a9d30c87318|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="MLB obit">{{cite news|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/don-sutton-dies-at-75|title=Hall of Famer Don Sutton dies at 75|first=Mark|last=Bowman|date=January 19, 2021|work=MLB.com|publisher=MLB Advanced Media|accessdate=January 19, 2021|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128062013/https://www.mlb.com/news/don-sutton-dies-at-75|dead-url=no}}</ref>

